1
00:00:49,184 --> 00:00:52,768
=In Love With Loving You=
(Based on Love by Erxi on Qimao)

2
00:00:52,768 --> 00:00:55,520
=Episode 4=

3
00:01:01,472 --> 00:01:03,296
(This Year's Autumn Semester
Aid Recipients)

4
00:01:03,296 --> 00:01:05,344
(Ji Xuan, Female, Environmental Art Design
Aid Amount: 2,000 RMB)

5
00:01:29,088 --> 00:01:32,192
(Ji Xuan, Female, Environmental Art Design
Aid Amount: 2,000 RMB)

6
00:01:52,599 --> 00:01:53,840
Hello, Mr. Zhang?

7
00:01:53,840 --> 00:01:55,920
Ji Xuan, I have some good news for you.

8
00:01:56,359 --> 00:01:59,359
Someone saw your profile
and decided to sponsor your education.

9
00:02:00,200 --> 00:02:02,640
Could you give me
his contact information?

10
00:02:02,680 --> 00:02:03,879
I want to thank him in person.

11
00:02:03,879 --> 00:02:06,879
It's anonymous.
He only left an email address.

12
00:02:06,959 --> 00:02:08,560
He said you can communicate via email.

13
00:02:08,919 --> 00:02:10,360
Okay, please send it to me later.

14
00:02:10,520 --> 00:02:11,280
Thank you, sir.

15
00:02:11,280 --> 00:02:11,919
You're welcome.

16
00:02:11,919 --> 00:02:12,439
Thank you.

17
00:02:51,759 --> 00:02:53,360
If you're creatively drained, go home.

18
00:02:53,719 --> 00:02:54,759
Don't waste my time.

19
00:02:56,120 --> 00:02:56,879
Who is she?

20
00:02:58,800 --> 00:03:01,080
- Why was she in Mr. Song's room?
- Yeah.

21
00:03:01,080 --> 00:03:01,759
Then Xie Yao...

22
00:03:06,048 --> 00:03:06,680
Go back.

23
00:03:16,479 --> 00:03:18,479
Take the day off today
to clear your head.

24
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:20,000
Redo it when your mind is clear.

25
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:20,960
- Yes.
- Yes.

26
00:03:22,319 --> 00:03:23,280
Quick, let's go.

27
00:03:24,840 --> 00:03:26,120
Who was that woman just now?

28
00:03:27,759 --> 00:03:28,800
What's it to you?

29
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:30,599
I'm your fiancée.

30
00:03:30,599 --> 00:03:32,080
You owe me an explanation.

31
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:33,360
Listen to me, Xie Yao.

32
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:35,599
Marry whoever you want.

33
00:03:36,280 --> 00:03:37,520
It has nothing to do with me.

34
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:40,479
Song Zhaoli! Song Zhaoli!

35
00:03:51,439 --> 00:03:54,400
I checked. You're the one
involved in that scandal, right?

36
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:56,319
You are...

37
00:03:58,199 --> 00:03:59,599
Did you often sleep your way up?

38
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:04,919
I'm Xie Yao, the marketing manager
of Song Corp.

39
00:04:05,280 --> 00:04:07,439
Technically, I'm also your client.

40
00:04:12,719 --> 00:04:15,400
So, Miss Xie,
what exactly do you want to say?

41
00:04:18,480 --> 00:04:20,560
Sorry, I didn't mean to.

42
00:04:26,560 --> 00:04:28,720
Sorry, I didn't mean to either.

43
00:04:32,839 --> 00:04:34,120
Let me be honest with you.

44
00:04:34,360 --> 00:04:35,920
I am Song Zhaoli's fiancée.

45
00:04:36,439 --> 00:04:38,199
You better know your place.

46
00:04:40,680 --> 00:04:42,079
I don't like Song Zhaoli.

47
00:04:42,160 --> 00:04:43,199
I'm not interested in him.

48
00:04:43,319 --> 00:04:45,160
You don't need to see me as your rival.

49
00:04:45,240 --> 00:04:46,600
You're not interested in him?

50
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:48,160
Then why did you sleep with him?

51
00:04:49,560 --> 00:04:50,920
I was just playing with him.

52
00:05:02,120 --> 00:05:02,959
Mr. Song?

53
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:04,600
Was it fun?

54
00:05:06,160 --> 00:05:07,160
Want to play some more?

55
00:05:56,079 --> 00:05:57,199
Are you crazy?

56
00:05:57,439 --> 00:05:58,720
You called me all the way here

57
00:05:58,800 --> 00:06:00,120
just to walk me like a dog?

58
00:06:00,439 --> 00:06:02,120
You're too weak. Practice abstinence.

59
00:06:03,439 --> 00:06:05,720
So aggressive.
Not working out as the other man?

60
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:08,240
Let's talk.
Master Liao's emotional counseling.

61
00:06:08,720 --> 00:06:09,759
I heal heartbreak.

62
00:06:11,160 --> 00:06:12,079
Have you been in love?

63
00:06:12,279 --> 00:06:13,040
Never.

64
00:06:13,519 --> 00:06:15,560
But I'm a groom every night.

65
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:22,360
(Ji Xuan)
(Sorry, Mr. Song.)

66
00:06:22,879 --> 00:06:24,319
(I want to explain it to you.)

67
00:06:24,560 --> 00:06:27,040
(I absolutely did not mean
to badmouth you behind your back.)

68
00:06:27,279 --> 00:06:29,000
(I hope you don't take it to heart.)

69
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:33,040
Are you pissed off, Mr. Song?

70
00:06:33,120 --> 00:06:34,120
Mind your own business.

71
00:06:35,920 --> 00:06:37,639
Does Ji Xuan know you were her sponsor?

72
00:06:37,639 --> 00:06:38,480
She doesn't know.

73
00:06:38,839 --> 00:06:39,439
Don't tell her.

74
00:06:39,800 --> 00:06:42,399
Impressive. Pure love, huh?

75
00:06:42,399 --> 00:06:44,600
You don't want Ji Xuan
to be with you out of gratitude.

76
00:06:44,879 --> 00:06:48,120
You spent money and effort,
yet you're hiding your contributions.

77
00:06:48,360 --> 00:06:50,800
You're truly a role model
for the other man.

78
00:06:51,319 --> 00:06:52,680
She doesn't need to know that.

79
00:06:54,319 --> 00:06:55,120
Song,

80
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:57,879
all these years,
I've actually wanted to ask you.

81
00:06:58,120 --> 00:06:59,519
Why did you sponsor Ji Xuan then?

82
00:07:01,079 --> 00:07:03,959
Do you remember
when my brother and I were kidnapped?

83
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:09,639
On my way back after being rescued...

84
00:07:10,944 --> 00:07:12,768
(IOU)

85
00:07:12,768 --> 00:07:13,888
(Debtor: Ji Jianye)

86
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:15,959
Ji Jianye borrowed money
to start a business

87
00:07:16,279 --> 00:07:18,480
and ended up ruining himself.

88
00:07:18,800 --> 00:07:20,040
But the debt remains.

89
00:07:20,680 --> 00:07:21,759
Listen to me.

90
00:07:22,079 --> 00:07:25,240
Today, whether you want to or not,
you two are paying it back.

91
00:07:25,240 --> 00:07:25,792
Stop the car.

92
00:07:26,439 --> 00:07:27,639
If you really have no money,

93
00:07:27,936 --> 00:07:29,184
pay for it with your place.

94
00:07:29,680 --> 00:07:31,360
- No.
- My dad left this place to us.

95
00:07:31,399 --> 00:07:32,240
I won't sell it.

96
00:07:32,600 --> 00:07:34,480
I'll pay back the money my dad owed you.

97
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:40,000
Do you think I'm stupid?

98
00:07:40,120 --> 00:07:42,360
How can a little girl like you
pay it back?

99
00:07:44,199 --> 00:07:45,120
Xuan!

100
00:07:47,519 --> 00:07:49,120
Either kill me today,

101
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:51,040
or we sign the contract.

102
00:07:51,079 --> 00:07:52,439
I will repay every cent

103
00:07:52,560 --> 00:07:55,319
of the money my dad owed you.

104
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:06,839
Xuan.

105
00:08:09,519 --> 00:08:11,879
You're tougher than me.
Fine, we'll do it your way.

106
00:08:12,079 --> 00:08:12,736
Let's go.

107
00:08:13,879 --> 00:08:14,680
Xuan?

108
00:08:15,040 --> 00:08:16,319
Mom, I'm fine.

109
00:08:17,720 --> 00:08:18,720
Xuan.

110
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:20,000
Let's go back.

111
00:08:24,680 --> 00:08:26,639
My brother died back then.

112
00:08:27,399 --> 00:08:28,480
I didn't want to live.

113
00:08:29,199 --> 00:08:32,399
But that girl, burdened with debt,
fought so hard to live.

114
00:08:35,840 --> 00:08:37,600
So you fell for her?

115
00:08:38,559 --> 00:08:39,159
I didn't.

116
00:08:39,480 --> 00:08:40,480
You didn't?

117
00:08:40,879 --> 00:08:42,000
But I heard

118
00:08:42,159 --> 00:08:44,879
that Ji Xuan came out of your room
this morning.

119
00:08:46,039 --> 00:08:47,120
I'm just having some fun.

120
00:08:49,056 --> 00:08:50,496
(Song Zhaoli)

121
00:09:14,879 --> 00:09:18,039
(Mr. Qiu, I think
I said the wrong thing to Mr. Song.)

122
00:09:18,240 --> 00:09:19,799
(Do you know where he is?)

123
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:21,080
(I want to apologize to him.)

124
00:09:22,559 --> 00:09:23,200
You may go back.

125
00:09:24,320 --> 00:09:27,279
I climbed over the rocks to get here.

126
00:09:29,159 --> 00:09:29,760
Alright.

127
00:09:43,879 --> 00:09:45,120
(Mr. Qiu)
(Mr. Song is at the beach.)

128
00:09:45,639 --> 00:09:47,600
(Location)
(You can go find him and cheer him up.)

129
00:09:48,159 --> 00:09:49,279
(Mr. Song isn't that petty.)

130
00:10:17,879 --> 00:10:19,919
Mr. Song. Mr. Song.

131
00:10:21,480 --> 00:10:22,279
What a coincidence.

132
00:10:22,720 --> 00:10:23,960
You like running too, Miss Ji?

133
00:10:26,320 --> 00:10:28,480
Why are you running in a suit?

134
00:10:29,639 --> 00:10:31,559
I came specifically to apologize to you.

135
00:10:31,759 --> 00:10:33,039
I misspoke this morning.

136
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:35,120
I'm sorry.
Please don't take it to heart.

137
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:37,799
Is this an apology to me

138
00:10:38,799 --> 00:10:40,000
or to your client?

139
00:10:42,559 --> 00:10:43,519
Is there a difference?

140
00:10:44,120 --> 00:10:45,039
The difference is huge.

141
00:10:50,480 --> 00:10:52,399
To me, there's no difference.

142
00:10:53,039 --> 00:10:55,080
You are my client, after all.

143
00:11:00,519 --> 00:11:03,159
How about this?
We run back to the hotel together.

144
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:05,440
If you're faster than me,
I'll forgive you.

145
00:11:07,488 --> 00:11:08,032
Okay.

146
00:11:38,644 --> 00:11:40,436
♪In the vast sea of stars♪

147
00:11:40,596 --> 00:11:42,476
♪Flickering neon lights♪

148
00:11:42,676 --> 00:11:46,004
♪Longing spreads
throughout the universe♪

149
00:11:46,516 --> 00:11:48,788
♪Every star is♪

150
00:11:49,076 --> 00:11:52,948
♪My heartbeat for you♪

151
00:11:54,260 --> 00:11:56,084
♪Want to ride the evening breeze♪

152
00:11:56,244 --> 00:11:57,796
♪And land in your arms♪

153
00:11:58,196 --> 00:12:01,652
♪The starry sky is like your eyes♪

154
00:12:01,908 --> 00:12:04,468
♪In the blue sky♪

155
00:12:04,532 --> 00:12:08,660
♪Your smile still lingers♪

156
00:12:09,588 --> 00:12:13,236
♪You are the brightest light
in my regrets♪

157
00:12:13,492 --> 00:12:17,156
♪You are the painful greeting
in my despair♪

158
00:12:17,364 --> 00:12:20,096
♪Can't find a cure♪

159
00:12:20,276 --> 00:12:24,788
♪To love you after we've parted♪

160
00:12:24,980 --> 00:12:29,012
♪You are the time I most want to keep♪

161
00:12:29,012 --> 00:12:32,768
♪The future I strive toward
in the darkness♪

162
00:12:32,768 --> 00:12:34,676
♪Slowly getting closer to you♪

163
00:12:34,772 --> 00:12:39,924
♪How I wish
I could give you my sunshine♪

164
00:12:40,564 --> 00:12:44,276
♪You are the brightest light
in my regrets♪

165
00:12:44,468 --> 00:12:47,220
♪Can't find a cure♪

166
00:12:47,348 --> 00:12:51,988
♪To love you after we've parted♪

167
00:12:52,156 --> 00:12:55,924
♪You are the time I most want to keep♪

168
00:12:56,148 --> 00:12:59,732
♪The future I strive toward
in the darkness♪

169
00:12:59,956 --> 00:13:01,888
♪Slowly getting closer to you♪

170
00:13:01,888 --> 00:13:06,996
♪How I wish
I could give you my sunshine♪
